dia cantik?

444
00:25:30,253 --> 00:25:33,023
Hei, dia cantik sekali.

445
00:25:39,933 --> 00:25:43,803
Itu karena ciuman pertama
Jung Saet-Byul.

446
00:25:44,333 --> 00:25:46,373
Ciuman itu?

447
00:25:46,433 --> 00:25:48,943
Dia langsung menciumku begitu saja.
Itu ciuman pertamanya?

448
00:25:51,313 --> 00:25:54,013
Astaga.
Hei, aku tak memercayai kalian.

449
00:25:54,283 --> 00:25:56,913
Kenapa dia menciumku?

450
00:25:57,183 --> 00:25:59,153
Apa dia menyukaiku?

451
00:25:59,213 --> 00:26:00,253
- Ya.
- Ya.

452
00:26:05,023 --> 00:26:05,993
Itu tidak benar, 'kan?

453
00:26:06,053 --> 00:26:08,963
Kami terkejut melihat dia menciummu.

454
00:26:09,263 --> 00:26:12,433
Karena kita berbagi rahasia,
mau kuberi tahu satu rahasia lagi?

455
00:26:12,493 --> 00:26:14,703
- Beri tahu dia.
- Ciuman pertama itu

456
00:26:15,163 --> 00:26:16,973
adalah ciuman terakhirnya!

457
00:26:18,503 --> 00:26:19,703
Kalau begitu...

458
00:26:20,443 --> 00:26:25,273
Tunggu. Setelah hari itu,
dia tidak pernah mencium siapa pun.

459
00:26:25,843 --> 00:26:27,813
Mungkin ada sarang laba-laba
di mulutnya.

460
00:26:30,913 --> 00:26:31,953
Astaga.

461
00:26:33,653 --> 00:26:34,723
Aku...

462
00:26:35,523 --> 00:26:36,623
Air...

463
00:26:41,123 --> 00:26:42,163
Tunggu.

464
00:26:44,363 --> 00:26:45,433
Pak Choi!

465
00:26:46,433 --> 00:26:49,033
